#  ██████╗ ██╗ ██████╗███████╗    ██╗███╗   ██╗███████╗████████╗ █████╗ ██╗     ██╗     ███████╗██████╗
#  ██╔══██╗██║██╔════╝██╔════╝    ██║████╗  ██║██╔════╝╚══██╔══╝██╔══██╗██║     ██║     ██╔════╝██╔══██╗
#  ██████╔╝██║██║     █████╗      ██║██╔██╗ ██║███████╗   ██║   ███████║██║     ██║     █████╗  ██████╔╝
#  ██╔══██╗██║██║     ██╔══╝      ██║██║╚██╗██║╚════██║   ██║   ██╔══██║██║     ██║     ██╔══╝  ██╔══██╗
#  ██║  ██║██║╚██████╗███████╗    ██║██║ ╚████║███████║   ██║   ██║  ██║███████╗███████╗███████╗██║  ██║
#  ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝ ╚═════╝╚══════╝    ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═══╝╚══════╝   ╚═╝   ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝╚══════╝╚══════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝
#
#   Author  -   gh0stzk
#   Repo    -   https://github.com/gh0stzk/dotfiles
#   Last updated  -  2025-03-24 (Artix s6 compatibility + LightDM bspwm session)
